title: Urgent Opportunity: Songcamp/Elektra - EXTENDED
body:
See the discussion here:
https://community.beetsdao.com/t/urgent-opportunity-songcamp-elektra/99

We have a very strong opportunity to win visually and musically stellar songs/art from the Songcamp Elektra auction ending in less than 24 hours.

The suggestion is to allocate up to 7 ETH to win or partybid. 

3 options in the vote:

Bid on 1/1: We will only bid to win outright ownership. If we do not win, we will keep 7 ETH
Partybid: We will partybid with others, we will own fractional rights, but all 7 ETH will be spent
Do not bid

Please read, listen and decide.
author: 0x0392c0D81934B52f64aA50C2cFbbcf28cd6141b2
